ethod on 407 subjects with MRI data from baseline Alzheimer’s Disease Neuroimaging Initiative (ADNI) database. The experimental results suggest that our MDL method achieves promising results in both tasks of hippocampus segmentation and clinical score regression, compared with several state-of-the-art methods. © 2018 Springer Science+Business Media, LLC, part of Springer Nature},
